    {
      question: 'What technology consulting services do you offer?',
      answer: 'We provide comprehensive technology consulting including digital transformation strategy, cloud migration, cybersecurity assessment, IT infrastructure modernization, software development, and technology roadmap planning tailored to your business needs.'
